<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>TRAVEL</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="travel.css" />
  </head>

  <body>
    <%- include('../../views/header'); %>
    <div class="w-full border-t-0 border-r-0 border-left-0">
      <div class="h-12"></div>
      <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full">
        <div class="w-full fixed z-20 bg-white shadow">
          <div class="container relative mx-auto">
            <div class="flex flex-row justify-end md:p-5 p-6">
              <div>
                <a
                  class="hidden md:inline-block mx-2 font-semibold"
                  href="/metropol-turizm"
                  >Anasayfa</a
                >
                <a class="hidden md:inline-block mx-2 font-semibold" href="#"
                  >Hakkımızda</a
                >
                <a class="hidden md:inline-block mx-2 font-semibold" href="#"
                  >İletişim</a
                >
                <div id="mobilemenu" class="z-40">
                  <img
                    class="block md:hidden w-6"
                    src="assets/img/mobilemenu.svg"
                    alt="mobile menu"
                  />
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div
              class="absolute flex flex-row justify-center w-full left-0 top-12"
            >
              <div class="-mt-6">
                <img
                  class="w-24 shadow"
                  src="assets/img/venntourlogo.png"
                  alt="venntour logo"
                />
              </div>
            </div>
            <div
              id="mobilemenu-container"
              style="opacity: 0; overflow: hidden"
              class="absolute flex flex-col items-center px-14 py-2 top-16 z-30 right-0 bg-red-50 md:hidden border-red-500 border-l-2"
            >
              <a
                href="/metropol-turizm"
                class="block my-3 font-semibold border-red-300 border-b-2"
                >Anasayfa</a
              >
              <a
                href="#"
                class="block my-6 font-semibold border-red-300 border-b-2"
                >Hakkımızda</a
              >
              <a
                href="#"
                class="block my-6 font-semibold border-red-300 border-b-2"
                >İletişim</a
              >
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <main>
      <div class="mt-4">
        <div
          class="relative bg-cover bg-center bg-no-repeat"
          style="height: 510px; background-image: url(assets/img/travel-cover.png)"
        >
          <div class="absolute bottom-6 flex justify-center w-full">
            <button
              class="transition duration-500 ease-in-out hover:bg-red-500 transform hover:scale-105 text-white font-semibold py-3 px-6 rounded-full"
              style="background-color: #ee2930"
            >
              Bilgi Al
            </button>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="container mx-auto mt-24 mb-12 px-4 md:px-0">
        <h1 class="font-bold text-bigTitle text-center mb-36 mt-3">TRAVEL</h1>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-between">
          <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 mt-6 md:mt-0">
            
            <p class="mb-2 text-content">
              Venn Travel olarak profesyonel ekibimiz ve uzman rehber kadromuzla misafir memnuniyetini en üst düzeyde tutarak, en geniş ürün yelpazesi ile ve standartların ötesine geçecek ufak dokunuşlarımız ile gerçekleştireceğimiz yurtdışı paket turlarımız çok yakında sizlerle.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="w-full md:w-1/3 flex justify-center">
            <img src="../../assets/img/dailytours-img.png" alt="Daily Tours" />
          </div>
        </div>
        <div
          class="flex flex-wrap-reverse items-center justify-between md:mb-32"
        >
          <div class="w-full md:w-1/3 flex justify-center">
            <img
              src="../../assets/img/packagetours-img.png"
              alt="Package Tours"
            />
          </div>
          <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 mt-6 md:mt-0">
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-4xl md:text-bigTitle mb-3">
              Ürünlerimiz
            </h4>
            <p class="mb-2">
             
              <ul>
                <li class="text-content">
                  Avrupa Turları
                </li>
                <li class="text-content">
                  Uzakdoğu Turları
                </li>
                <li class="text-content">
                  Asya Turları
                </li>
                <li class="text-content">
                  Afrika Turları
                </li>
                <li class="text-content">
                  Güney Amerika Turları
                </li>
                <li class="text-content">
                  Tematik Turlar
                </li>
                <li class="text-content">
                  Exclusive Turlar
                </li>
              </ul>
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </main>

    <script src="travel.js"></script>
  </body>
</html>
